可能地打造这款游戏。</p><p>上一届独立世界展示会<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=brNLmMMB-J4">于 9 月举办</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/how-to-watch-nintendo-direct-september-2023-3497834">任天堂直面会大</a>获成功，其中包括<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/five-nights-at-freddys-security-breach">《玩具熊的五夜后宫：安全漏洞》、《</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/oxenfree-2-lost-signals">OXENFREE II：丢失信号》、《</a></em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cult-of-the-lamb"><em>羔羊崇拜：旧信仰遗迹》</em></a>​​和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bomb-rush-cyberfunk">《炸弹狂潮 Cyber​​funk》</a></em>等。 </p><figure id="attachment_3486667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3486667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3486667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cult-of-the-lamb-dont-starve-together-crossover-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3486667" class="wp-caption-text"> 《羔羊崇拜》来源：Devolver Digital</figcaption></figure><p>此次展示之际，多家媒体最近声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/nintendo-switch-2-demoed-with-a-souped-up-breath-of-the-wild-alleges-report-3494729">任天堂在 Gamescom 2023 闭门会议上展示了 Nintendo Switch 2</a> 。</p><p>据报道，该控制台用于运行<a href="https://www.