00px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/david-bowie">大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a>在 1982 年改编的<em>《雪人》</em>的著名介绍中所佩戴的雪人围巾的复制品现已可供购买。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/tv-blogs/lets-remember-david-bowies-forgotten-intro-snowman-1920311">让我们都记住大卫·鲍伊被遗忘的《雪人》前奏</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://notjustclothing.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NotJust Clothing</a>品牌推出以雪人世界为主题的圣诞系列<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />品牌商品。其中一些单品包括节日套头衫、围巾和毛毯，其灵感源自雷蒙德·布里格斯 (Raymond Briggs) 最受欢迎的标志性图画书<em>《雪人》(The Snowman</em> )，该书于 1978 年首次出版。</p><p>这条传奇围巾的售价为 19.99 英镑，灵感源自鲍伊在拍摄<em>《雪人》</em>简介时在自家阁楼上佩戴的那条围巾，当时动画首次在美国播出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="雪人 - 鲍伊介绍 - 高清" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/54MEWWIiIk8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>多年来，深受喜爱的圣诞动画的粉丝们一直在寻找这件衣服，鲍伊的儿子邓肯·琼斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/producer-shares-heartwarming-story-behind-david-bowie-the-snowman-scarf-2845119">去年重新发现了原来的围巾</a>。</p><p>制作鲍伊电影简介的布莱恩·哈丁 (Brian Harding) 在 X/Twitter 帖子中分享了琼斯发现这条围巾背后的故事。</p><p> “围巾是动画制作公司TVC会计部的女士编织的。她来到片场并将其呈现给大卫。拍摄结束后，大卫非常有礼貌地询问是否可以保留这条围巾送给他的儿子佐伊，”他写道。</p><p>故事继续说道：“这是他为拍摄收取的唯一费用，我相信他出于个人原因提供服务。他自始至终都很迷人而且非常专业。我很高兴这条围巾到达了他想要的目的地：从一个家伙到另一个家伙。” </p><figure id="attachment_3537748" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3537748" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3537748" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image.jpg" alt="不仅仅是服装“雪人”系列。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Snowan-Collection-image-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3537748" class="wp-caption-text">不仅仅是服装“雪人”系列。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>在新闻稿中谈到此次合作和标志性单品时，Notjust 创始人 Mike Harding 表示：“我们带着庆祝全国最受欢迎的圣诞动画<em>《雪人》</em>的官方系列回归。”</p><p>他继续说道：“如果没有他，圣诞节就不一样了，我们非常自豪能够与雪人团队合作，让已故雷蒙德·布里格斯的标志性圣诞人物永垂不朽，他在每个节日期间都温暖着全国人民的心，优质、精心制作的针织品，每次销售都会回馈慈善事业。”</p><p>每笔销售的 50% 收益将捐赠给圣巴拿巴临终关怀医院（以栗子树屋儿童临终关怀医院名义经营），这是雷蒙德·布里格斯 (Raymond Briggs) 的朋友和赞助人的慈善机构。</p><p>在鲍伊的其他新闻中，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Cure">The Cure</a>鼓手 Lol Tolhurst 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lol-tolhurst-on-his-new-book-goth-a-history-the-cure-david-bowie-3500575">分享了鲍伊的《Low》如何成为他和罗伯特·史密斯的模板</a>。</p><p> Speaking to <em>NME</em> , Tolhurst said: “I can remember going to a party when I was 19, hearing &#39;Sound and Vision&#39; and thinking this is <em>everything</em> I want a pop single to be because it&#39;s catchy, it&#39;s lovely but it&#39;s also much deeper and darker.”</p><p> He continued: “I was watching people and thinking it&#39;s great to dance to and it makes you feel good, but there&#39;s something more there too. I knew that was what I wanted to do with music. I wanted to do something that was accessible but can give you that feeling as well. Bowie&#39;s &#39;Low&#39;<em> </em>was a template for me and I know it was for Robert as well. We played Bowie songs a lot when we started. I still listen to &#39;Low&#39; probably once every couple of weeks.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iconic-the-snowman-david-bowie-scarf-now-for-sale-3537718">Iconic &#39;The Snowman&#39; David Bowie scarf now for sale</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
